<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>접근 권한이 없습니다 - AI 로또 분석</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/5/w3.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            min-height: 60vh;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #9c27b0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .error-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .home-button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        .login-button {
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .login-button:hover {
            background-color: #1976D2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../ins/top') %>
    
    <div class="w3-container">
        <div class="error-container">
            <div class="error-code">403</div>
            <div class="error-message">접근 권한이 없습니다</div>
            <div class="error-description">
                이 페이지에 접근할 권한이 없습니다.<br>
                관리자 로그인이 필요하거나 다른 계정으로 로그인해주세요.
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="/" class="home-button">
                    <i class="fa fa-home"></i> 메인 페이지로 이동
                </a>
                <a href="/signin_up" class="login-button">
                    <i class="fa fa-sign-in"></i> 로그인
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../ins/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
